Fix random_step boundary

Fix random_step boundary

As buffer size in do_loop() is FIPS_RNG_BUFFER_SIZE, so the random_step should not bigger.
If random_step > FIPS_RNG_BUFFER_SIZE,  update_kernel_random() will not write any date.
